item.description: About I am a Junior at The University of Texas at Austin pursuing a BSA in Biology and a minor in communication studies. I have participated in Freshmen Research Initiative for two years, working on an independent project to select for an aptamer. In addition I am a marketing intern for PrideBites in Austin. I am proffiecient in Microsoft Office suites and R studio.
